   Economy:
   Manufacturing
   Sector Shows
   Signs of Upturn
   ---
   Purchasing Group's Index
   On Orders, Output, Jobs,
   Rose to 51.1% for June
   ----
   By Hilary Stout
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/03/90
</DATE>
